              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "-ISOMERIC YIELD RATIOS OF 134-I AND 136-I AND",
                " INDEPENDENT FRACTIONAL YIELDS OF SOME HALOGEN ISOTOPES",
                " IN THE FISSION OF 232-TH WITH REACTOR NEUTRONS."
              ]
            }
          ],
